name: 'Delfin'
description: Animated video of 3D scanned dolphin shaped slide in Brasov, Romania. The slide reportedly has around 40 years of age. It has been used by many generations of children and this is why it is the subject of nostalgia and affection. It passed well the test of time. 'Delfin' is a way to conserve the memory and honor the object that still rests in the central park of Brasov.
